{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro Relics</strong> is a cozy sandbox and story-driven <strong>treasure hunting simulation</strong>, where you immerse yourself into nature and search for ancient artifacts with your metal detector. Explore, dig, help other people find lost belongings and complete your coin and relics collection. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/DetectAndFind.png?t=1739382063\" />You can unearth artifacts from all epochs with the help of your metal detector: coins, buttons, buckles, jewellery, military, religious relics and many more </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/DetectingLoop600.gif?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/PinpointerMinigame600.gif?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/ExploreNature.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the mysteries of ancient ruins, explore lush forests, dusty fields and relax on a treasure hunt at the beach! Many animals can be spotted on your adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/NewRuinsFrontal.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/HelpOtherPeople.png?t=1739382063\" />Go on numerous search missions for the local people in your town, including a sad dog owner, a strange hunter and a sophisticated archeologist trying to decipher ancient ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/CompleteCollection.png?t=1739382063\" />Collect more than 100 different artifacs and display them in your cozy homestead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Find over 100 hand-pixeled artifacts varying from modern trash to ancient gold relics: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/Relics.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate your personal museum and display your rarest and prettiest finds:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/Museum.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/HelpAnimals.png?t=1739382063\" />People don't only lose treasures - help nature by picking up trash and watch animals come back to their former habitats </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/trashcollecting.gif?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/TurtlesReturn.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/PrepareHunt.png?t=1739382063\" />At your cozy homestead you can: sell artifacts, accept new missions via email, manage your collection, upgrade your gear</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/Inhouse600.gif?t=1739382063\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About me:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I'm Jonas, 31 years old, from Germany. I'm a solo developer working on Retro Relics in my free time. I'm a passionate metal detectorist myself and have many years of experience in the hobby. Many of the relics you can undig in the game, I have found myself in real life. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/Gardentree600.gif?t=1739382063\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join the community</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you want to take part in the development of Retro Relics, have feedback or ideas for the game, you are very welcome to my small Discord community:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/extras/Community.png?t=1739382063\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3072760?t=1739382063","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3072760?t=1739382063","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/482ff9fb591f04b872bf5ee2832f0549215093e8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739382063","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072760/482ff9fb591f04b872bf5ee2832f0549215093e8/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739382063","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro Relics</strong> is a cozy sandbox and story-driven <strong>treasure hunting simulation</strong>, where you immerse yourself into nature and search for ancient artifacts with your metal detector. Explore, dig, help other people find l